---
// Flexible Learning Access component
---

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Flexible Learning Access</h2>
    <div class="content-text">
      <p>Dao-Yu-101 offers different ways to access learning content.</p>
      
      <div class="access-options">
        <div class="access-option">
          <h3>Single Lessons</h3>
          <p>Students can purchase individual lessons to learn specific topics.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="access-option">
          <h3>Subscription Access</h3>
          <p>Subscriptions unlock complete archipelagos and allow students to explore multiple topics and subjects.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="access-explanation">This flexible system allows learners to progress at their own pace.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .content-section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248,250,252,0.95), rgba(241,245,249,0.85));
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: #1f2937;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .content-text {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .content-text p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .access-options {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
    margin: 30px 0;
  }

  .access-option {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.3);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .access-option h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: #059669;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .access-option p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .access-explanation {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #7f8c8d;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content-text {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .access-options {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .access-option {
      padding: 20px 15px;
    }

    .access-option h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .access-option p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>